canonical:
  title: 忠世
  author: 南孝溫
  language: lzh
  text: 携兒散步歷山陂紅杏梢頭月午時半死心隨春意動臨風折得最繁枝
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 忠世
  author: 南孝溫
  language: lzh
  text: 携兒散步歷山陂。紅杏梢頭月午時。半死心隨春意動。臨風折得最繁枝。
korean:
  title: 살구꽃 필 때에 시골집에 있었다. 어느날 밤에 달을 타고 충세
  author: 남효온
  language: kor
  text: |-
    아이들과 산보하여 메 언덕 지나치니
    붉은 살구 가지 위에 달이 휘영청
    반나마 늙은 마음 봄을 따라 움직이어
    번화한 가지는 바람 맞아 꺾었노라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0300&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Apricot Blossoms
  author: Nam Hyo-on
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Walking with my children past the ridge of Lisan,
    red apricot branches bask in moonlit noon.
    My half-withered heart stirs with the spring's desire—
    I break the flowering branch that bends before the wind.
  footnotes:
    - 'Lisan (歷山): A legendary sacred mountain, here used to evoke a timeless rural setting.'
    - The 'half-withered heart' suggests the speaker's middle age, caught between the fading of old age and the rekindling of vitality through spring's awakening.
